{
  "page": "Manfred Lothston",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">It is unknown whether this character and <a href=\"/index.php/Manfryd_Lothston\" title=\"Manfryd Lothston\">Manfryd Lothston</a> were the same person.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lothston\" title=\"House Lothston\"><img alt=\"House Lothston.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/50px-House_Lothston.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/75px-House_Lothston.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/100px-House_Lothston.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Manfred Lothston</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lothston\" title=\"House Lothston\"><img alt=\"House Lothston.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/50px-House_Lothston.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/75px-House_Lothston.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b3/House_Lothston.svg/100px-House_Lothston.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lothston\" title=\"House Lothston\">House Lothston</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafmanfred_lothston.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafmanfred_lothston.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Manfred Lothston</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lothston\" title=\"House Lothston\">House Lothston</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manfred_Lothston&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Manfred sided with <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon I Blackfyre\">Daemon Blackfyre</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"First Blackfyre Rebellion\">First Blackfyre Rebellion</a>, but betrayed him in the end.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manfred_Lothston&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafmanfred_lothston.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafmanfred_lothston.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Manfred Lothston.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403164152\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.069 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.275 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 493/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10510/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5681/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 370/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1398/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.65 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  265.923      1 -total\n 87.43%  232.498      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 86.65%  230.417  